Key Features

User Authentication & Management

Powered by Clerk, providing a secure and scalable user authentication system out of the box. Supports roles and permissions, allowing for easy differentiation between regular users and admins.

Comprehensive Admin Dashboard

Intuitive dashboard for managing listings, sponsorships, and ads without needing to dive into the code. Admins can easily add, edit, approve, or delete listings, ensuring full control over the directoryâ€™s content.

Integrated Stripe Payments

Seamlessly integrated with Stripe for handling payments, enabling easy monetization of listings and sponsorships. Secure payment processing with customizable flows, including one-time payments or subscriptions.

Supabase-Powered Backend

Uses Supabase for data storage, offering real-time updates and scalability with a familiar SQL interface. Pre-configured API routes for creating, retrieving, updating, and deleting listings.

Responsive & Modern Design

Built with Tailwind CSS, offering a clean, modern, and fully responsive design that looks great on all devices. Easy to customize, allowing you to quickly match the design to your brand's identity.

Advanced Search Functionality

Powerful search capabilities enabling users to find listings quickly based on categories, keywords, and other filters. Optimized for performance, ensuring fast load times even with large datasets.

Fully Customizable

Flexible and extendable codebase, making it easy to add new features or modify existing ones. Tailor the look and feel with just a few tweaks in the configuration files.

Quick Setup & Deployment

Simple setup process with detailed documentation, allowing you to deploy your directory quickly. Compatible with popular deployment platforms like Vercel for fast and seamless deployment.

SEO Optimized

Structured to follow SEO best practices, helping your directory rank higher in search engine results. Built-in meta tags, sitemap, and schema markup for enhanced visibility.

One-Time Payment, Lifetime Access

Pay once and get lifetime access to the codebase, with no recurring fees or hidden costs. Regular updates and support to ensure your directory stays up-to-date with the latest web standards.
